Main engine start.

1612
01:55:54,880 --> 01:55:55,996
<i>eight...</i>

1613
01:55:56,360 --> 01:55:57,360
<i>seven...</i>

1614
01:55:57,520 --> 01:55:59,159
<i>Mooring clamps released.</i>

1615
01:55:59,320 --> 01:56:00,913
About five seconds, Watney.
Hang on.

1616
01:56:01,080 --> 01:56:02,753
I'll see you in a few,
Commander.

1617
01:56:03,040 --> 01:56:04,360
<i>four...</i>

1618
01:56:04,760 --> 01:56:06,035
<i>three...</i>

1619
01:56:06,320 --> 01:56:07,515
<i>two...</i>

1620
01:56:07,920 --> 01:56:08,956
<i>one.</i>

