01:56:45,240 --> 01:56:47,630
Velocity, 741 meters per second.

1622
01:56:47,800 --> 01:56:49,757
Altitude, 1350 meters.

1623
01:56:49,920 --> 01:56:51,070
That's too low.

1624
01:56:51,240 --> 01:56:52,390
It's fighting me.

1625
01:56:56,240 --> 01:56:59,472
<i>Watney, do you read?</i>

1626
01:57:05,480 --> 01:57:06,755
<i>Booster separation complete.</i>

1627
01:57:06,920 --> 01:57:09,958
Velocity, 850.
Altitude, 1843.

1628
01:57:10,160 --> 01:57:11,355
He's well below target altitude.

1629
01:57:11,520 --> 01:57:12,749
How far below?

1630
01:57:13,280 --> 01:57:14,350
Checking.

1631
01:57:14,960 --> 01:57:16,155
Watney.

1632
01:57:16,800 --> 01:57:17,800
Do you read?

1633
01:57:18,080 --> 01:57:19,275
<i>He's probably passed out.</i>

1634
01:57:19,440 --> 01:57:20,590
<i>He pulled 12 g's on the ascent.</i>

1635
01:57:20,720 --> 01:57:21,949
<i>Give him a few minutes.</i>

1636
01:57:22,120 --> 01:57:23,270
<i>Copy that.</i>

1637
01:57:25,640 --> 01:57:26,960
<i>Main shutdown in three...</i>

1638
01:57:27,640 --> 01:57:29,199
<i>two, one...</i>

1639
01:57:29,920 --> 01:57:30,990
<i>shutdown.</i>

1640
01:57:32,560 --> 01:57:34,040
<i>Back to automatic guidance.</i>

